### Travel Agent Chatbot — quick checks from Cursor
### REST Client extension: choose env "local" or "render" (footer); edit render baseUrl in .vscode/settings.json if needed.

### Health (matches Render healthCheckPath)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Chat smoke (expects JSON body from API)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What is your refund policy?"
}

### Booking lead config (true when BOOKING_LEAD_URL or knowledge integrations URL is set)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/public/booking-lead-config

### Create lead (fails with 503 if no webhook URL configured)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/leads
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "source": "smoke",
  "trip": {
    "origin": "JFK",
    "destination": "JED",
    "departure_date": "2026-06-14",
    "adults": 1,
    "currency": "USD"
  },
  "fare": {
    "rank": 1,
    "total_price": 100.0,
    "currency": "USD"
  }
}
